                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>In a telegram of May 15 to Secretary-General Lie, Moshe Shertok, signing as
                    Foreign Secretary of the Provisional Government of Israel, applied for admission
                    of the State of Israel to membership in the “family of nations”; for text, see
                        <gloss target="#t_SC1">SC</gloss>, <hi rend="italic">3rd yr., Supplement for
                        May 1948</hi>, page 88.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
